001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.GraphQLQuery;
004import java.lang.Override;
005import java.lang.String;
006import java.util.Currency;
007import java.util.HashSet;
008import java.util.Set;
009
010public class ShippingMethodsByLocationGraphQLQuery extends GraphQLQuery {
011  public ShippingMethodsByLocationGraphQLQuery(String country, String state, Currency currency,
012      String queryName, Set<String> fieldsSet) {
013    super("query", queryName);
014    if (country != null || fieldsSet.contains("country")) {
015        getInput().put("country", country);
016    }if (state != null || fieldsSet.contains("state")) {
017        getInput().put("state", state);
018    }if (currency != null || fieldsSet.contains("currency")) {
019        getInput().put("currency", currency);
020    }
021  }
022
023  public ShippingMethodsByLocationGraphQLQuery() {
024    super("query");
025  }
026
027  @Override
028  public String getOperationName() {
029     return "shippingMethodsByLocation";
030                    
031  }
032
033  public static Builder newRequest() {
034    return new Builder();
035  }
036
037  public static class Builder {
038    private Set<String> fieldsSet = new HashSet<>();
039
040    private String country;
041
042    private String state;
043
044    private Currency currency;
045
046    private String queryName;
047
048    public ShippingMethodsByLocationGraphQLQuery build() {
049      return new ShippingMethodsByLocationGraphQLQuery(country, state, currency, queryName, fieldsSet);
050               
051    }
052
053    public Builder country(String country) {
054      this.country = country;
055      this.fieldsSet.add("country");
056      return this;
057    }
058
059    public Builder state(String state) {
060      this.state = state;
061      this.fieldsSet.add("state");
062      return this;
063    }
064
065    public Builder currency(Currency currency) {
066      this.currency = currency;
067      this.fieldsSet.add("currency");
068      return this;
069    }
070
071    public Builder queryName(String queryName) {
072      this.queryName = queryName;
073      return this;
074    }
075  }
076}
